RACE.FOOTNOTES: ABOVE THE FOLD engaged with MIRAGE CODE in the early running and disputed a decent pace with that rival into the turn, pressed inside of MIRAGE CODE along the turn, shook free of that rival and assumed command into upper stretch, was kept to task under steady urging to the sixteenth-marker, was confronted in deep stretch by BETTOR BET'R, gamely dug in in the final strides and lasted for the win at the finish.
